title: Slender frog
text:
The slender frog ("Austrochaperina gracilipes") is a species of <a href="frog">frog</a> in the family <a href="Microhylidae">Microhylidae</a>.
It is found in Australia and <a href="New%20Guinea">New Guinea</a>.
Its natural <a href="habitat">habitat</a>s are subtropical or tropical dry <a href="forest">forest</a>s, subtropical or tropical <a href="swamp">swamp</a>s, moist <a href="savanna">savanna</a>, <a href="river">river</a>s, and intermittent rivers.
